佢佢都未必教你<br />\n<br />\n睇你有冇心學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87243ee6812eb7ee9ecaba84ac12bbe43542b8b7","tid":2247674,"uid":339440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"人生5星星咪得囉"},{"pid":"821d1645014b9d57637443c0b3fae911b6be83a8","tid":2247674,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"問老母"},{"pid":"43fcda53c7533d5fedfdf2a930929387a56025f1","tid":2247674,"uid":93000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"搵paper睇 如果你係做research <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab34423e88ca817c80a1615b27e32900917c6f8b","tid":2247674,"uid":243351,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"我會扮睇得明"},{"pid":"9dea4285650568b215ee2e83f93c40bb90a50058","tid":2247674,"uid":63336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03c294f9ab2e825d9615fbe53e4b88a5d198792e","tid":2247674,"uid":93060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"如果有1段 甚至成PART睇唔明 可能因為英文差 又可能因為未理解某d concept/唔夠人生歷練去理解<br />\n你地會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接skip個part 遲d再睇番  定係會慢慢磨到睇得明為止<br />\n明明本書已經相對地淺白易明 唔知點解再重睇個part都係唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"好難講一個方法，我會有幾個方向。<br />\n1）繼續睇，作者嘅寫作思路未必對每一個讀者都係通順。睇埋後面，可能會明翻啲前面講嘅野，不停咁前後，前後睇一般都掌握到個脈絡。<br />\n2）有時到真係完全跟唔到就轉睇其他野。過一段時間，再試過。有時只係需要停一停，補充翻啲腦力，再試多幾次就讀得通。如果一個grand idea 俾你一次就讀通，咁你自己都無癮啦。<br />\n3）如果真係讀好多次都係無進展，咁可能真係時機未成熟去睇。有啲概念需要配合外在因素（例如：時代背景去）理解，正如你同一個2020年讀緊書嘅中/大學生講佢係proletariat, 佢會好似明個theory 講咩，但實際上後面果一串理念佢未必掌握到。<br />\n4）另外，你講語文能力一定有影響。如果作者表面上係話你知講緊個蘋果，但係因為語文差累，讀者理解咗佢講緊西瓜，咁好難會跟得到作者個思維。"},{"pid":"d40c3c3fd4006f8aeace17a9d77095544c4e43d5","tid":2247674,"uid":347278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"藍色窗簾"},{"pid":"bdd4b98ebbf8368136aaede9dc8ce0faac476af7","tid":2247674,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6365b41c34fe453f89bf561e796c28e391e6ae3c","tid":2247674,"uid":431,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"會去瞓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bd00115fd1307b83984459c9e994f61b9963c4","tid":2247674,"uid":281775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"兩樣可能皆可<br />\ndepends on<br />\n1. 份文有幾重要 好緊要/要做功課當然要睇 否則冇時候磨的就飛<br />\n2. 段嘢有幾重要 try to get the points/concepts/use of the paragraph<br />\n3. 要知自己唔明乜 如果係當中一些concept的backgroud 去IEP甚至wiki briefly get the idea 如果係英文句complicate then 拆句 eliminate some adj clause/that clause<br />\n4. 老土話 睇得多就會熟和快 睇得多本身都係練習/過程 哲學文係真係難明的"},{"pid":"3e413301f4b1efebc6b4ddbc8e634bb5b190153d","tid":2247674,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f31c08cde96776c9a973252b4fd69575c1cfc706","tid":2247674,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"你唔係玩野既話 去問蕭生個fd 陶國璋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SvBv_W3davQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSvBv_W3davQ&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=d0c55fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SvBv_W3davQ</a><br />\n<br />\n呢到 <br />\n<br />\n教哲學既    平時佢教書都好平凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似當朋友吹水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"蕭生識親都勁人<br />\n<br />\n物以類聚 <br />\n<br />\n好明白個差距<br />\n<b